ContentDesc_Anabaseios - Zwölfter Kreis: While Nemjiji is plainly in awe at your bravery and relieved that the realm is saved once more, she seems almost disappointed in your descriptions of the chief keyward's prowess in battle. As you finish your recounting she lets out a despondent sigh before perking up and taking up her quill with aplomb, muttering to herself, “Nothing a little imagination cannot fix...”
Instancecontenttextdata_13901_Text: Denizens of the abyss! From ink of blackest night, I summon you! Darkness to me!
Instancecontenttextdata_36901_Text: Show me your all, that I might become divinity manifest!
Instancecontenttextdata_36903_Text: These chains are forged from the fabric of creation!
Instancecontenttextdata_36904_Text: To silent vessels, I give voice!
Instancecontenttextdata_36905_Text: This is but a glimpse of a god's strength!
Instancecontenttextdata_36906_Text: Behold such power as you will never wield!
Instancecontenttextdata_36907_Text: From the deepest pit of the seven hells to the pinnacle of the heavens, the world shall tremble!
Instancecontenttextdata_36913_Text: What arrogance to defy a god!
Instancecontenttextdata_36914_Text: Could my theories have been flawed...?
Instancecontenttextdata_36916_Text: But perhaps...with the Heart of Sabik!
Instancecontenttextdata_36919_Text: Only the hands of a god can fix it─my hands!
Instancecontenttextdata_36920_Text: I can create worlds─or unmake them!
Instancecontenttextdata_36921_Text: Only I can guide this star to its rightful place!
Instancecontenttextdata_36923_Text: Denizens of the abyss! From ink of blackest night, I summon you!
Instancecontenttextdata_36924_Text: Misfortune hangs heavy on the prideful. Poor cover for when the heavens fall.
Instancecontenttextdata_36925_Text: From base elements is greatness forged!
Instancecontenttextdata_36926_Text: The wheel of life turns by my hand!
Instancecontenttextdata_36927_Text: The elements flow according to my design.
Instancecontenttextdata_36928_Text: Creation's course is mine to set!
Instancecontenttextdata_36932_Text: Why do you suffer this pathetic existence!?
